Cs_number13 - A map by AnTwanChi

Terrorists having taken scientists from FearCorp hostage in an empty house that happens to be number 13. People of a pagan disposition would argue that the number 13 is a lucky number. Play this map and find out for yourselves!

Many thanks to all of those people who I've unwittingly taken textures and models from.

Go to rustyinplaces.org and play this on our css server!

Special thanks to Bearbison and the whole of [RIP] Rustyinplaces clan. The best clan in the world!
